{"tid":1637480,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼聯戰績插水 蘇斯克查：責任在我","createTime":"2019-10-08T03:59:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T13:26:17.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fbdf9d35b344ddbcdd72fa100c5a8d347043a012","tid":1637480,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:59:32.000Z","msg":"曼聯昨日以0：1敗於紐卡素腳下，球隊開季至今得分仍未達雙位數。主帥蘇斯克查承認球隊表現差勁的責任在他身上，會藉國際賽期的機會整頓球隊。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯戰績低迷，領隊蘇斯克查自然成為球迷「開火」對像，這名挪威主帥亦承認自己要為此負責：「我們表現很叫人失望。我們確有幾個主力球員不能上陣，但這也不是藉口。球員在場上已盡了力，但我們確未有創造足夠的機會。幸運的是即將踏入國際賽期，我們有時間檢討過去8戰的表現，希望之後有些球員可以復出。這是我的責任，我應理清一班年輕球員的思緒，他們仍欠缺經驗及信心。」<br />\n<br />\n曼聯目前在英超8戰僅得9分，若於國際賽期後不能及時回勇，相信蘇斯克查的帥位亦難言安穩。（<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIlcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=35a232a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>）"},{"pid":"157209b35af1178d748802b59f68107298e9e45c","tid":1637480,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:59:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/ad8cfada7f461d837d22b1b15d29bc6e/tumblr_pyyw6xXK4J1qc85nuo1_500.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2Fad8cfada7f461d837d22b1b15d29bc6e%2Ftumblr_pyyw6xXK4J1qc85nuo1_500.gifv&h=db07aac8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4fb2525961b6d738f8cf2a76549a7b20a123b0b6","tid":1637480,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:09:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/72312375_10157925460018598_3905114415917170688_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_oc=AQnnYRjYuKI3xrEhoBK1woCWRWdHWfdiy1he_K6xzEzc3TzJVfOLwRutz8FKlWEmd7M&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=55dda5d859742bd69a91724bbf8cb12b&amp;oe=5E2BE1D0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F72312375_10157925460018598_3905114415917170688_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_oc%3DAQnnYRjYuKI3xrEhoBK1woCWRWdHWfdiy1he_K6xzEzc3TzJVfOLwRutz8FKlWEmd7M%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D55dda5d859742bd69a91724bbf8cb12b%26oe%3D5E2BE1D0&h=28388fd8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b4c5c02f8c9ac460f0770c399986dfb4c1e4d4f","tid":1637480,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:26:17.000Z","msg":"落地獄死全家未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}